# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Notes:
# - `.gradle/`, `build/`, `run/` have no leading slash, so they match at every
#   depth (root AND versions/<node>/...), covering Stonecutter's per-version
#   generated directories.
# - versions/<node>/gradle.properties are SOURCE files (dependency versions and
#   loom.platform) and MUST stay tracked — do not ignore them.
# - gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar is intentionally NOT ignored (no *.jar
#   rule) so `gradlew` keeps working after clone.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
